  "summary": "SGLang: Unauthenticated RCE via --enable-custom-logit-processor",
  "details": "SGLang's multimodal generation runtime is vulnerable to unauthenticated remote code execution when the --enable-custom-logit-processor option is enabled, as Python objects loaded via dill.loads() will be deserialized without validation.",
